author: Amanda House, Amanda House
title: Watch Live: Minnesota Workers Protest Outside Governor’s Mansion
description: Hundreds of Minnesotans plan to protest outside Governor Tim Walz's residence Friday to demand an end to the state's stay-at-home order.
content:
Hundreds of Minnesotans plan to protest outside Governor Tim Walz’s residence Friday to demand an end to the state’s stay-at-home order.
